text: Suzanne J. Crough (March 6, 1963 - April 27, 2015) was an American actress best known for her role as Tracy Partridge, from the hit television sitcom The Partridge Family, which ran from September 25, 1970 until March 23, 1974. Crough was born in Fullerton, California. She was married and had two daughters. Crough died on April 27, 2015 at her home in Laughlin, Nevada from cardiomyopathy, aged 52. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1963 births Category:2015 deaths Category:Deaths from cardiomyopathy Category:Actors from Orange County, California Category:American child actors Category:American television actors Category:American voice actors Category:Disease-related deaths in Nevada
